Second Department,

September, 1943.

(September 16, 1943.) In the Matter of Elizabeth B. Fitzpatrick, Appellant, against Walter W. Westall et al., Constituting the Board of Elections of the County of Westchester, et al., Respondents.

No opinion. Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals granted. Close, P. J., Hagarty, Carswell, Taylor and Lewis, JJ., concur.
